name: Over the Plains of America
description: This image, "Over the Plains of America" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to reflect the vast plains in America (USA). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in the process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
